</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_326" id="162v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_326_r2l15"><expan>VVılh<ex>elm</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Sawnſh<ex>eim</ex></expan> vogt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l16">cʒü Spekfelt / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_326_r2l17">Lıeber her vogt / Als Jr vns nechſt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> des geleittes </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l18"><expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / ob vvir ıht offner vehe heten / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l19">wir ew / daʒ vviſſen <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . Alſo <expan>laʒʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l21">wiſſen / daʒ wir 
<add><ab facs="#facs_326_r2l20">ew </ab></add> cʒü der cʒeit <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>nyema<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> me </del> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> wıſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l24">
<add><ab facs="#facs_326_line_1588335198891_1367">cʒe </ab><ab facs="#facs_326_r1l1">ſchreıben </ab></add> <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_326_r2l23"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> Gilbrecht <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Büchıs / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> deʒ </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_326_line_1576493216283_9221"><expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> </ab></add> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Kere / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_326_r2l22"><expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Tümfelt </ab></add> vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough"> dıe </del> <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l26"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Perlaching<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_326_r2l25">vnd Jren hellffern </ab></add> / <expan>Ab<ex>er</ex></expan> es iſt <expan>yecʒu<ex>n</ex>d<ex>en</ex></expan> ein gütlıch ſteen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l28"><expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns vnd den <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Perlaching<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_326_r2l27">bis auf Mauricij </ab></add> . Dann vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l29"><expan>bıtt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr ew die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> geleitte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l30">auf vnd abe beuolhen <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein / vnd ſie <expan>fürſeh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l31">Als wir ew getrawen vnd vormals auch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l32">vnd <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vj̃ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l33"><expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Egıdij / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_326" id="162v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Sawnsh<ex>eim</ex></expan>, vogt czü Spekfelt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her vogt, als ir uns nechst <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> des geleittes
                                <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, ob wir iht offner vehe heten, daz
                        wir ew daz wissen <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>solt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, also <expan>lazze<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wissen, daz wir <add>ew</add> czü der
                        czeit <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>nyema<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> wissen <add>cze schreiben</add>,
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan></add> Gilbrecht <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        Büchis, <add><expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan></add>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Kere, <add><expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Tümfelt</add> und
                            <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Perlaching<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add>und iren hellffern</add>. <expan>Ab<ex>er</ex></expan> es ist
                                <expan>yeczu<ex>n</ex>d<ex>en</ex></expan> ein gütlich steen
                                <expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns und den
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Perlaching<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add>bis auf Mauricii</add>. Dann wir <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ewr
                                <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>, daz ir ew die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        geleitte auf und abe bevolhen <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> sein und sie
                                <expan>fürseh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet, als wir ew getrawen und
                        vormals auch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Egidii.</ab>
</div>
